parameters.name: IncludeDeprecated
parameters.description:
Specifies whether to return deprecated secret versions.

Valid values:

*   false: no
*   true: yes

Default value: false.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: 10.
